{"text_id":255295,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," a"," semi","-","empi","rical"," pressure","-","volume","-","temperature"," equation"," of"," state"," for"," Mg","SiO","3"," per","ovsk","ite",","," an"," important"," mineral"," in"," the"," Earth","'","s"," mantle","."," The"," equation"," of"," state"," is"," used"," to"," describe"," the"," relationship"," between"," the"," pressure",","," volume",","," and"," temperature"," of"," the"," mineral"," and"," is"," critical"," for"," understanding"," the"," material","'","s"," behavior"," under"," extreme"," conditions","."," ","\n\n","The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," is"," twofold","."," First",","," accurate"," equations"," of"," state"," are"," crucial"," for"," interpreting"," experimental"," and"," theoretical"," data"," on"," mantle"," minerals","."," Second",","," the"," equation"," of"," state"," of"," Mg","SiO","3"," per","ovsk","ite"," has"," remained"," uncertain"," for"," many"," years",","," presenting"," a"," significant"," challenge"," to"," the"," geophysical"," community","."," Our"," work"," aims"," to"," overcome"," this"," challenge"," by"," providing"," a"," semi","-","empi","rical"," equation"," of"," state"," that"," is"," both"," accurate"," and"," consistent"," with"," available"," experimental"," data",".","\n\n","To"," achieve"," this"," goal",","," we"," combine"," existing"," experimental"," data"," with"," high","-","pressure"," computations"," using"," density"," functional"," theory","."," Our"," approach"," involves"," fitting"," a"," semi","-","empi","rical"," equation"," of"," state"," to"," the"," computed"," data",","," which"," provides"," a"," more"," accurate"," description"," of"," the"," mineral","'","s"," behavior"," at"," high"," pressures"," and"," temperatures","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," new"," equation"," of"," state"," accurately"," reproduces"," experimental"," data"," and"," provides"," a"," means"," to"," predict"," the"," behavior"," of"," Mg","SiO","3"," per","ovsk","ite"," under"," extreme"," conditions",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," our"," work"," presents"," a"," significant"," step"," forward"," in"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," behavior"," of"," Mg","SiO","3"," per","ovsk","ite"," and"," will"," help"," to"," improve"," our"," knowledge"," of"," the"," Earth","'","s"," mantle","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}